snippet.title: The Coma 2 (WT) - Teaser
snippet.description:
We've got a very special announcement this Halloween. 

We've already started work on the next project due for completion in 2019. The sequel of our very first game, The Coma: Cutting Class, is now in the works. 

Stay tuned!
